installation:

-clone/download repo (master branch)
- install requirements.txt using command "pip install -r requirements.txt"
- go to the main directory
- run command "python app.py"
go to http://127.0.0.1:5000/ in your browser to access the app

# RAG logic is in AUG.py file



misc-
if you want to change knowledge document, add pdf to the same directory and then decomment last line in  AUG.py with new title.
